{"serial": "43032", "department_serial": 41, "code": "IM6041", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Production and Operations Management", "ch": "生產與作業管理"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Chen, Jen-Ming"], "ch": ["陳振明"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 1, "session": ["2", "3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "I1", "room": "404"}}], "isRequired": true, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 75, "department": {"ch": "資訊管理學系", "en": "Department of Information Management"}, "system": {"ch": "碩博同修", "en": "Master/Doctoral Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 0, "selected": 73, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "“生產與營運管理(P＆OM)是在滿足顧客需求之前提下，對整個生產及供應網路（包含供應商、製造商、配銷商、零售商到消費者等）的規劃與運籌機能進行有效的綜合管理，其中涵蓋的運籌活動有採購、生產、運輸、配送、物料及倉儲等營運機能，經由對這些機能及活動進行系統優化的設計、規劃、協調、操作及控制，將正確產品、正確數量、在正確時間遞送到正確地點，並使總成本或總效益達到最佳化之目標。\n本課程將探討在供應鏈架構下之營運、工業4.0、智慧製造等先進技術相關管理議題，使用教材包含管理文獻、實務個案、影片等多樣教材，並配合學生報告、課堂研討、心得寫作及實作練習等方式進行，授課內容包含營運/智慧製造/供應鏈與永續管理之相關議題及生產活動之規劃、協調、操作及控制，同時兼論其在企業經營的策略意涵，以達成如下課程目標：（一）修課學生將了解營運/智慧製造/供應鏈/永續與社會責任的相關活動，包含作業面、戰術面及策略面之管理意涵，（二）修課學生將會使用基本的資訊、軟體、AI或解析工具(analytic tools)來解決智慧製造、SCM及永續相關營運問題，（三）修課學生將具有前瞻性、永續性的觀點來處理P＆OM所衍生的企業社會責任(CSR/ESG)及智慧系統等當代經營管理議題。“", "en": "“This course will introduce concepts and techniques for design, planning and control of manufacturing and service operations. The course provides basic definitions of operations management terms, tools and techniques for analyzing operations, and strategic context for making operational decisions. We present the material in three modules:\n1. Supply chain management\n2. Reversed and closed-loop supply chain management\n3. Sustainable supply chain management, Corporation Social Responsibility, and ESG issues in operations management\n4. Smart manufacturing/service system management, big data analytics“"}, "outline": {"ch": "“1.課程簡介與評分\n2.作業與供應鏈管理內容回顧\n3.專題報告：1 Factory operation/SCM, 2 Service management, 3 Value chain management, 4 Contracted manufacturer management, 5 Supply chain management, 6 Share value, 7 Globalization management, 8 Sustainable SCM, 9＆10 Sustainability and CSR (I ＆ II)\n4.課程回顧 Review of current issues on green ＆ sustainable supply chains“", "en": "“1.課程簡介與評分\n2.作業與供應鏈管理內容回顧\n3.作業與供應鏈管理之經營與策略議題： mission, vision, and value\n4.專題報告：1 Factory operation/SCM, 2 Service management, 3 Value chain management, 4 Contracted manufacturer management, 5 Supply chain management, 6 Share value, 7 Globalization management, 8 Sustainable SCM, 9＆10 Sustainability and CSR (I ＆ II)\n5.課程回顧 Review of current issues on green ＆ sustainable supply chains“"}, "textbook": {"ch": "“1 Stevenson (2021) Operations Management\n2 Harvard Business Review“", "en": "“1 Stevenson (2021) Operations Management\n2 Harvard Business Review“"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "50", "en": "50"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討\n\n個別指導\n其他", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar", "", "Individual Instruction", "Others"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "“出席 0％\n課程參與 20％\n作業、小考、心得寫作 20％\n同儕評論、評審 20％\n文獻專題＆計畫報告 40％“", "en": "“Class participation 0％\nClass engagement 20％\nHomework and exam 20％\nReport and presentation 40％\nPresentation review 20％“"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "12-2pm Monday", "en": "12-2pm Tuesday; 12-1pm Friday"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "第17-18週彈性教學為個別指導時間", "en": "Individualized instruction during weeks 17-18"}, "domain": {"ch": "商管知識", "en": "商管知識"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "原創性", "rating": "(2)低", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "熟悉其專業領域文獻", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現", "學習檔案評量", "自我評量/同儕互評"]}, {"competencies": "獨立思考和解決問題能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現", "學習檔案評量", "自我評量/同儕互評"]}, {"competencies": "溝通能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現", "學習檔案評量", 